Quickstrike:






Quickstrike took the coordinates in mind, trying to map it 
already. "Ah'll make sure ah's get t' it and bring whatever it is 
back jus' fer ya." He blinked slowly at Black Arachnia and grinned. 
He turned his body and glanced at Dark Mouse. "Say how 'bout you an' 
me go out there an' get his thing."
